OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772820365
OL,3,CDrone footage reveals charred remains
OL,4,Cof phone mast destroyed by fire
OL,6,FDrone footage has revealed the extent
OL,7,Fof damage to a phone mast in Oxford
OL,8,Fwhich was destroyed by fire.
OL,10,FThe charred remains of the mast which
OL,11,Fis located near the A40 can be seen
OL,12,Ffrom the sky.
OL,14,FFirefighters were called on Thursday
OL,15,Fevening and sent fire engines from
OL,16,Fthree different stations to the mast
OL,17,Fon Elsfield Way.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
