OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772820365
OL,3,CDrone footage reveals charred remains
OL,4,Cof phone mast destroyed by fire
OL,6,FThe service has now handed the
OL,7,Fincident over to the
OL,8,Ftelecommunications company that is
OL,9,Fresponsible for it.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Oxfordshire Fire
OL,12,Fand Rescue said: "Firefighters
OL,13,Fcordoned off the area, extinguished
OL,14,Fthe fire and monitored the temperature
OL,15,Fover several hours before handing the
OL,16,Fincident over.
OL,18,F"Investigations are underway into the
OL,19,Fcause of the fire."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
